		<div id="comment_body_64206192">CA, esp with idiot Newsom leading the way followed by total idiots like drink, worked hard to kill of SONGs, and now Diablo. At last second, Newsom decided to not let Diablo die , most likely because it will harm his run for president. Yet, we are sending CA 1B to extend certificate for another 5 years, then it shuts down. Yet, Diablo is rated to continue until 2060+. Note that Diablo provides more than 25% of CA&rsquo;s clean electricity, along with 25% of Bay Area drinking water ( cheaper than the reservoirs with run-off). However, Diablo is capable of not only providing 100+% of Bay Area water within 2 years ( leaving the natural water to be sent into the valley or even to southern
CA, BUT, it can de-carbonate sea water cheaper than the approach being taken for de-carbonating the atmosphere ( cold  water holds 26x the CO2 that atmosphere has; it is released as water is heated ).<br>
Now, the far left shut down palisades, but wants 1.5B to restart it for a short term. So, 2.5B for the far left to restart their fudge-ups for short terms. <br> <br>No. this is a horrible waste of federal $ ( like the subsidies for HICE, EVs and EV charger). Instead, 2.5b is enough to restart 2+ companies on building NEW SMR power plants. <br>
Restarting and accelerating the nuclear power industry is far more useful than throwing money at short-term restarts . At the very least, we need to require that these go long-term, provide clean water AND remove CO2 from the water.</div>
	</div>

